PN,34801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782134325
OL,3,CCourier who delivered weapons to
OL,4,Ccriminal gang jailed
OL,6,FA man who supplied dangerous weapons
OL,7,Fto the drug-dealing head of a
OL,8,FBirmingham-based crime group has today
OL,9,Fbeen jailed for more than 10 years.
OL,11,FRizwan Malik, 43, of Small Heath,
OL,12,Fsupplied crime boss Danyal Aziz with
OL,13,Fthree Walther Creed 9mm self-loading,
OL,14,Fsemi-automatic pistols.
OL,16,FMalik was jailed today after a trial
OL,17,Fat Birmingham Crown Court.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
