OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782134325
OL,3,CCourier who delivered weapons to
OL,4,Ccriminal gang jailed
OL,6,FAziz's group was responsible for
OL,7,Fflooding the West Midlands and other
OL,8,Fareas across the UK with huge
OL,9,Fquantities of class A drugs (heroin
OL,10,Fand cocaine) in 2020.
OL,12,FMalik was directed via Encrochat, an
OL,13,Fencrypted communications network used
OL,14,Fby criminals, to attend an address at
OL,15,FSapphire Heights, Hockley, which the
OL,16,Forganised crime group used as a base,
OL,17,Fto hand over three pistols in April
OL,18,F2020.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782134325
OL,3,CCourier who delivered weapons to
OL,4,Ccriminal gang jailed
OL,6,FCCTV footage captured Malik arriving
OL,7,Fin his van and meeting with one of
OL,8,FAziz's associates Michael Earp, 35,
OL,9,Ffrom Shard End, to transfer the
OL,10,Ffirearms.
OL,12,FAziz was sentenced to 33 years in
OL,13,Fprison in October 2023 for charges
OL,14,Fwhich included possessing the three
OL,15,Fweapons with intent to endanger life.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
