OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782134325
OL,3,CCourier who delivered weapons to
OL,4,Ccriminal gang jailed
OL,6,FEarp and another one of Aziz's
OL,7,Fassociates Nicole Rhone, 32, from
OL,8,FBordesley Green, were sentenced at the
OL,9,Fsame time ` Earp to 26 years for drugs
OL,10,Fand firearms offences and Rhone to 5
OL,11,Fyears for firearms offences.
OL,13,FThe gang was also in possession of
OL,14,Fother lethal weapons including a
OL,15,FSkorpion submachine gun which was
OL,16,Ffound stashed under a bed.
OL,18,FGiorgina Venturella, Specialist
OL,19,FProsecutor from the Crown Prosecution
OL,20,FService, said:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,349,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F348A1782134325
OL,3,CCourier who delivered weapons to
OL,4,Ccriminal gang jailed
OL,6,F"Malik put lethal weapons into the
OL,7,Fhands of an organised criminal, Danyal
OL,8,FAziz, who was fully prepared to use
OL,9,Fthem. This could have had potentially
OL,10,Fcatastrophic consequences for innocent
OL,11,Fmembers of the public.
OL,13,FAdding that he played an integral role
OL,14,Fin the whole enterprise, "handing this
OL,15,Fcriminal group the means to threaten
OL,16,Fand intimidate rivals and customers
OL,17,Falike, which was an intrinsic part of
OL,18,Ftheir operating model."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
